casebody.data:
Barry Stephen SWAIN
v.
Dorlene Davenport SWAIN. No. 590P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 27, 2007. John M. Martin, Greenville, for Stephen Swain. Jonathan Silverman, Sanford, for Dorlene Swain. Prior report: 179 N.C.App. 795 , 635 S.E.2d 504 .

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed on the 20th day of November 2006 by Plaintiff in this matter for discretionary review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 27th day of June 2007."
